RunSynchronousCommand.Path: cmd.exe /c ">>"X:\diskpart.txt" echo CREATE PARTITION EFI SIZE=300"
cmd.exe /c ">>"X:\diskpart.txt" echo FORMAT QUICK FS=FAT32 LABEL="System""
cmd.exe /c ">>"X:\diskpart.txt" echo CREATE PARTITION MSR SIZE=16"
cmd.exe /c ">>"X:\diskpart.txt" echo FORMAT QUICK FS=NTFS LABEL="Windows""
cmd.exe /c "diskpart.exe /s "X:\diskpart.txt" >>"X:\diskpart.log" || ( type "X:\diskpart.log" & echo diskpart encountered an error. & pause & exit /b 1 )"
cmd.exe /c ">>"X:\disable-defender.vbs" echo For Each drive In fso.Drives"
cmd.exe /c ">>"X:\disable-defender.vbs" echo For Each folder In Array( "$Windows.~BT\NewOS\Windows", "Windows" )"
cmd.exe /c ">>"X:\disable-defender.vbs" echo file = fso.BuildPath( fso.BuildPath( drive.RootFolder, folder ), "System32\config\SYSTEM" )"
cmd.exe /c ">>"X:\disable-defender.vbs" echo If fso.FileExists( file ) And fso.FileExists( file + ".LOG1" ) And fso.FileExists( file + ".LOG2" ) Then"
cmd.exe /c ">>"X:\disable-defender.vbs" echo If Not initialized Then"
cmd.exe /c ">>"X:\disable-defender.vbs" echo ElseIf Not dic.Exists( file ) Then"
cmd.exe /c ">>"X:\disable-defender.vbs" echo ret = shell.Run( "reg.exe LOAD HKLM\mount " + file, 0, True )"
cmd.exe /c ">>"X:\disable-defender.vbs" echo For Each service In Array( "Sense", "WdBoot", "WdFilter", "WdNisDrv", "WdNisSvc", "WinDefend" )"
cmd.exe /c ">>"X:\disable-defender.vbs" echo ret = shell.Run( "reg.exe ADD HKLM\mount\ControlSet001\Services\" + service + " /v Start /t REG_DWORD /d 4 /f", 0, True )"
cmd.exe /c ">>"X:\disable-defender.vbs" echo ret = shell.Run( "reg.exe UNLOAD HKLM\mount", 0, True )"
